<br>
I know this is wrong thinking and this is what is destroying me, but it is how I feel.  I don't know how you get past it.  I don't know how you just forgive.  I don't want to forgive .. I want them to suffer as I have suffered.  This is my own self-created hell and I know it.  Sometimes I think I could just settle for my mom admitting what my father has already admitted to .. she says my sister and I forced him to admit things he never did because we are jealous of her.  What is really sad is she is jealous of us .. she hates me and my sister because my father preferred us.  How sick is that?  Forgive? She is crazy too .. obviously.  Doesn't make it forgivable to me though.<br>
<br>
She is the mother.  She is suppose to be the protector.  She should never have allowed things to happen and here she is in such complete and total denial.  It is kinda weird but my father sexually abused me and admitted it in front of my mom.  I have forgiven him.  I don't feel anger to him now.  My mom who refuses to believe what she heard and even blame me and my sister for anything that might have happened has me so angry I seriously some days think I could do her harm. <br>
<br>
